race.description: Farm Frites Mcc Country Series Heat Handicap
race.comment: FLYING FIZZ (4) presents third up here and ready to fire. Two runs back have been solid in better company, battling home late into fifth at Caulfield last time in a BM78. Back a notch now, her form on the country circuits in these sorts of races has her firmly on top. GUERITE (12) is a progressive sort who resumed with a handy win at Geelong over a smart one in Rohesia. She's never missed the placings in six starts and should strip fitter up in trip. GUNADO (11) has been going okay of late and now steps up in trip which could suit. I CATCHEM FOX (5) next best. Won first up at Mt Gambier and bar one blip at Morphettville third up has generally been sound since.
